You also addressed the issue of snares and evacs. Keep in mind our snare is AE, meaning we have to have high MR so not snare ourselves. Also the fact, rangers, druids, warriors, necros, sk's and bards can all snare. And they can do it either without mana useage, or can have some other benefit while snareing. Warriors can do dmg with the snare whip, druids and rangers have gaunts, necro's and sk's can do dmg, bards can still twist songs with it. So why does th ewizard have to be the only class to get shafted, having to snare and do no other benefit in that 2 some odd seconds? And if you think wizards shouldn't get better because we get ae, then so do druids right? <br>
But all in all, i agree Armok.<br>
